<title>Chisʋs pi Okchalinchi ma! ƲIT126</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chisʋs pi Okchalinchi ma!
 Pi okchalinchi chi bʋnnʋt,
 Yakni ilʋppa ish la cha,
 Hatak ilbʋsha pulla 'k o̱.

[V2]
 Ʋba anumpa hanta ya̱,
 Yakni paknaka ilʋppa
 Ant ish boyuhli tok oka,
 E chithana mak inlishke.

[V3]
 Mikmʋt ʋba yakni 'chukma,
 Aiokpuloka aiena
 Ish pim anoli tok ona,
 E haha̱klot pi yukpʋshke.

[V4]
 Chisʋs Klaist holitopa ma!
 Na̱ chi yimmi puta pia
 Shilombish Holitopa ya̱
 Ish pi nukfoki pullashke.

[V5]
 Ish pi apela pulla na,
 Chi̱ hullot, chim antihiiyʋt,
 Chim ai a̱hli bilia hosh,
 Itʋnoho̱wʋt pillashke.</lyrics>
</song>